 Contributing
We welcome contributions! See CONTRIBUTING.md for guidelines.

# Contributing to German Legal Summarizer

Welcome! This project aims to make German legal documents more accessible through AI summarization. We welcome contributions from developers, legal professionals, and AI enthusiasts.

## Contribution Areas

### 1. Improving Model Performance
- Add more training data (German legal documents with summaries)
- Experiment with different base models
- Implement better preprocessing for legal texts
- Add support for more document types (laws, court decisions, etc.)

### 2. Expanding Language Support
- Add support for other languages (French, Spanish, etc.)
- Improve English summarization quality
- Add translation capabilities

### 3. Enhancing Features
- Add document structure analysis
- Implement key clause extraction
- Add risk assessment features
- Create API for integration with legal software

### 4. Improving Usability
- Better web interface
- Batch processing capabilities
- Integration with cloud storage
- Mobile app development

## Getting Started

### Development Environment
1. Fork and clone the repository
2. Set up Python 3.10+ environment
3. Install dependencies:
   ```bash
   pip install -r requirements.txt
